Paper: hep-th/9507043

Date: 1995-07-07

Title: BRST Analysis of QCD_2 as a Perturbed WZW Theory

Authors: D.C. Cabra, K.D. Rothe, F.A. Schaposnik

Comments: 14 pages, LaTeX

Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A11 (1996) 3379-3391

Integrability of Quantum Chromodynamics in 1+1 dimensions has recently beensuggested by formulating it as a perturbed conformal Wess-Zumino-Witten Theory.The present paper further elucidates this formulation, by presenting a detailedBRST analysis.